feat: add Shadcn UI styles and Tailwind CSS configuration
- Introduced a new CSS file for Shadcn UI styles with CSS variables for theming. - Updated Tailwind CSS configuration to support dark mode and added container queries. - Enhanced typography and spacing utilities for better responsiveness. - Added custom utilities for text shadows, gradients, and glassmorphism effects. - Improved scrollbar styling and added new animation keyframes. - Updated type definitions to use `unknown` instead of `any` for better type safety. - Refactored JSON-LD processing logic to improve type handling and validation. - Cleaned up imports in graph analytics module. - Added TypeScript build info files for app and node configurations.
